name: Translated Texts for Historians E-Library
description: Translated Texts for Historians (TTH) book series makes available historical sources from 300-800 AD translated into English, in many cases for the first time. The Translated Texts for Historians E-Library now offers this invaluable collection as a digital library, containing over 60 volumes from the series that bring together a wealth of important historical texts with scholarship from leading academics.
